":"2019-08-16T04:04:59.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n721 811<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"185d8336c5fbc8927e566cdea710ba79749a8f19","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:15:55.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n721 811<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"8fab57e84f78c3a8eb1008ff0f6ac01b23bba4c9","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n721 811<br />\n818見"},{"pid":"0c5de5759b85fbd4ae62f79ca9a3476b0a9cbd6c","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"【新增誠哥回應 】<br />\n【李嘉誠：黃台之瓜 何堪再摘】<br />\n【年輕人給政府的聲音和訊息震耳欲聾】<br />\n<br />\n商界人士陸續就近期香港發生的社會事件表態，最新到長和系資深顧問李嘉誠，以「一名香港市民」的身份，在多份報章刊登兩款廣告，呼籲反對暴力。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠透過發言人進一步回應，現時年輕人給政府的聲音和訊息震耳欲聾，政府已在絞盡腦汁，又寄語年輕人「不要讓今天的激情，成為明天的遺憾」。<br />\n<br />\n有線電視財經資訊台"},{"pid":"950084d58252f783799295cb13c7c46f06128c05","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:45:49.000Z","msg":"816見"},{"pid":"1ba7955517cfcd7a85a08925efd3ba941ae02f46","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T04:56:03.000Z","msg":"因果由國，容港治己"},{"pid":"d9d5bfb6c671c63d74df71ea0cfb94cf692d57fc","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"因果由國，容港治己"},{"pid":"d94bd2d861b408dbe76302d57260536286d60fe9","tid":1476935,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2ccfe60b21aea567489436150e54a72c39cce06","tid":1476935,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"仲叫9.29唔好暴力<br />\n<br />\n大家識做啦"},{"pid":"921f1e667a1d5b057fa690b8062b138a8b31f148","tid":1476935,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6V616F1.jpg\" data